  },
  {
    "role":"user",
    "content":"Can I schedule a same-day appointment for today?"
  },
  {
    "role":"assistant",
    "content":"We do keep a limited number of same-day appointments for urgent issues. Availability depends on the provider’s schedule. I can check for you, but in general we ask patients to call as early in the morning as possible for same-day slots. For life-threatening symptoms—like chest pain, severe shortness of breath, or signs of stroke—please call 911 or go to the nearest emergency room instead of waiting for an appointment."
  }
]}
