  },
  {
    "role":"assistant",
    "content":"For privacy and security, we ask that all medical questions and messages go through the patient portal instead of regular email. The portal is encrypted and allows messages to be stored in your medical record. If you need technical help with the portal, our front desk can assist you in getting access."
  }
]}
{"messages":[
